nmap <C-k>e :cs find e <C-R>=expand("<cword>")<CR><CR>:bel copen<CR><CR>	
nmap <C-k>f :cs find f <C-R>=expand("<cfile>")<CR><CR>:bel copen<CR><CR>	
nmap <C-k>i :cs find i ^<C-R>=expand("<cfile>")<CR><CR>:bel copen<CR><CR>	
